OL,5,G1000 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe first visit is to The Bell
OL,7,     FHouse Hotel in Wiltshire, where
OL,8,     Fowners Chris and Jacqui aim to
OL,9,     Fbring London chic to the shires.
OL,10,     FBut their absence at breakfast
OL,11,     Fprovokes criticism.
OL,12,G1035 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe second visit is to The
OL,14,     FPartridge in Oxfordshire, where
OL,15,     FMatthew Cockman and Paula
OL,16,     FSzkwarkowska share a passion for
OL,17,     Forganic food. But the self-service
OL,18,     Fbreakfast has the guests up in
OL,19,     Farms.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
