OL,5,G1105 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe third visit is to Strawberry
OL,7,     FGardens B&B in Heysham, where
OL,8,     FDavid and Susan Speak aim to make
OL,9,     Ftheir guests feel at home with
OL,10,     Fnorthern hospitality. But Paula
OL,11,     Fsends back her evening meal.
OL,12,G1135 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe last visit is to The Bateman's
OL,14,     FMill near Chesterfield, where Jade
OL,15,     FHendon and Diana Yates aim to be
OL,16,     Fthe best, but David and Susan are
OL,17,     Fquick to find hairs in the
OL,18,     Fbathroom.
