OL,5,G1210 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FIt's payment day, and fur flies as
OL,7,     FJade tackles Matthew over feedback
OL,8,     Ffor The Bateman's Mill. The group
OL,9,     Fthrash out their differences
OL,10,     Fbefore the winner is revealed.
OL,11,G1240 Come Dine with Me
OL,12,     FWinchester. Live wire Ptol is
OL,13,     Fconvinced that high-quality food
OL,14,     Fand fine wine will win him the
OL,15,     Fprize. But his guests find his
OL,16,     Fmenu underwhelming and his hosting
OL,17,     Fstyle over the top. (Ep1/5)
