OL,5,G1520 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe first hosts, Karen MacDonald
OL,7,     Fand Geoff Thomson, hope to offer a
OL,8,     Fslice of Zen at their relaxing
OL,9,     Fretreat, Just B, in Edinburgh. But
OL,10,     Fthere are dirty discoveries in a
OL,11,     Fdog-friendly room.
OL,12,G1550 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe second visit is to Glencoe
OL,14,     FVilla Guest House in Featherstone,
OL,15,     FWest Yorkshire, owned by Ewa Hunt.
OL,16,     FBut the homely bedrooms aren't to
OL,17,     Feveryone's taste and there's a
OL,18,     Fdebate over dinner.
