OL,5,G1620 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FUncle and nephew Stefan Carron and
OL,7,     FNick Edwards host at The Fox Inn
OL,8,     Fin Stourton, Staffordshire. Will
OL,9,     FStefan's celebrity name dropping
OL,10,     Fimpress their guests?
OL,11,G1650 Four in a Bed
OL,12,     FTony Carlin and his partner
OL,13,     FNatalie Briggs host the final
OL,14,     Fvisit, at The New Inn in
OL,15,     FDerbyshire. But some of the guests
OL,16,     Fquestion its 'luxury' label, and
OL,17,     Fthere's a no-show at breakfast.
