OL,5,G1855 Location, Location, Location
OL,6,     FIn Southampton, Kirstie helps
OL,7,     FAntoinette and Matt revive their
OL,8,     Fattempts to get on the property
OL,9,     Fladder. And Phil's with Catherine
OL,10,     Fwho wants a fresh start in
OL,11,     Fcharming Chichester.
OL,12,G1955 Grand Designs
OL,13,     FWhen he lost three limbs in
OL,14,     FAfghanistan, Jon's life changed
OL,15,     Fforever. Now he wants to build a
OL,16,     Fhouse that allows him to live
OL,17,     Findependently. The design's
OL,18,     Fcutting edge, but the budget
OL,19,     Fspirals.
