OL,5,G2100 Bill Bailey's Vietnam
OL,6,     FIn Hanoi, Bill explores Vietnam's
OL,7,     Fcomplex relationship with life,
OL,8,     Fdeath and war, and a culture
OL,9,     Fdefined by spirituality and
OL,10,     Ffemininity, and remembers the
OL,11,     Fpeople who he's lost. (Ep4)
OL,12,G2200 Bill Bailey's Remarkable Guide...
OL,13,     F...to the Orchestra: Let Bill be
OL,14,     Fyour guide as he joins forces with
OL,15,     Fmaestro Anne Dudley and the BBC
OL,16,     FConcert Orchestra for a humorous
OL,17,     Ffusion of music and comedy at the
OL,18,     FRoyal Albert Hall.
